title: New runtime api to check if a validator has pending pages of rewards for an era.

doc:
  - audience: Node Dev
    description: |
      Creates a new runtime api to check if era reward is pending for a validator. Era rewards are paged and this api
      will return true as long as there is one or more pages of reward not claimed.

